Packet
The Packet class is the way the information is stocked to transit between the Client and Server The format is the following: [(int) request, (string) content] If more than one item need to be added in a packet, add ";" in the content to separate them Example: Packet p = new Packet(1, "Jean;12345") If you want to modify the behaviour notably to do it in JSON, feel free to do.
